 Each scalar in the unrotated chunk is shifted back by the\noptimized lag, and the lag-corrected chunk is written as its own 30-minute\nfile, with the original header rows and column order preserved.","position":{"start":{"line":64,"column":1},"end":{"line":64,"column":1}},"key":"DpcpvCRbGW"}],"key":"DRQeznF2oo"}],"key":"FxW9ncV3e2"}],"key":"BkCdd6FIHH"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":68,"column":1},"end":{"line":70,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Outputs land in the output directory: the lag-corrected 30-minute files, a\nsummary table (","position":{"start":{"line":68,"column":1},"end":{"line":68,"column":1}},"key":"v242a1vmZn"},{"type":"inlineCode","value":"1_lag_detection/detect_and_remove_tlag_summary.csv","position":{"start":{"line":68,"column":1},"end":{"line":68,"column":1}},"key":"bi9VhNIWVT"},{"type":"text","value":"), optional\noverview plots, and a ","position":{"start":{"line":68,"column":1},"end":{"line":68,"column":1}},"key":"e4Shs9Uhjj"},{"type":"inlineCode","value":"log.txt","position":{"start":{"line":68,"column":1},"end":{"line":68,"column":1}},"key":"MTooEmxWSX"},{"type":"text","value":" of the run.","position":{"start":{"line":68,"column":1},"end":{"line":68,"column":1}},"key":"OwaaoFWPtf"}],"key":"V8orsNsmQ1"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":72,"column":1},"end":{"line":73,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The lag-corrected files then go through normal flux processing with EC time-lag\nmaximization disabled, because the tube delay has already been corrected here.","position":{"start":{"line":72,"column":1},"end":{"line":72,"column":1}},"key":"T1DJBOo5zJ"}],"key":"eNC2yIQug1"}],"key":"D2KIxwtZtq"}],"key":"b7bfzhOygV"},"references":{"cite":{"order":["vitale2024"],"data":{"vitale2024":{"label":"vitale2024","enumerator":"1","doi":"10.1007/s10651-024-00615-9","html":"Vitale, D., & others. (2024). TODO: verify exact article title (pre-whitening with block-bootstrap time-lag detection). <